(185, '2026-07-06', 'Spirit of Liberty', '{"reference":"2 Corinthians 3:17","text":"Now the Lord is the Spirit, and where the Spirit of the Lord is, there is freedom."}'::jsonb, 'Today, let the peace of God rule in your heart. Whatever challenges you face, remember that His presence goes with you. Trust in His unfailing love and walk confidently.', '["Lord, give me a grateful heart","Help me to see Your hand in every situation","Let praise continually be on my lips"]'::jsonb, '["My faith pleases God","Mountains move at my command","I speak and things happen"]'::jsonb, 'Moses Afolabi'),
(186, '2026-07-07', 'Free Indeed', '{"reference":"John 8:36","text":"So if the Son sets you free, you will be free indeed."}'::jsonb, 'God''s promises are yes and amen. Every word He has spoken over your life will come to pass. Hold onto hope, for the One who promised is faithful.', '["Father, protect me from the schemes of the enemy","Cover me with Your precious blood","Station Your angels around me"]'::jsonb, '["I am healed by His stripes","Divine health is my portion","Sickness has no place in my body"]'::jsonb, 'Moses Afolabi'),
(187, '2026-07-08', 'Captives Released', '{"reference":"Luke 4:18","text":"He has sent me to proclaim freedom for the prisoners."}'::jsonb, 'The Lord is working behind the scenes on your behalf. What seems like delay is divine preparation. Trust His timing and His methods.', '["Lord, heal every area of brokenness in my life","Restore what the enemy has stolen","Make me whole in Jesus'' name"]'::jsonb, '["Abundance flows to me","My needs are met according to His riches","I am a generous giver"]'::jsonb, 'Moses Afolabi'),
(188, '2026-07-09', 'Walking in Liberty', '{"reference":"Psalm 119:45","text":"I will walk about in freedom, for I have sought out your precepts."}'::jsonb, 'You are more than a conqueror through Christ. Every obstacle is an opportunity for God to show His power. Face today with boldness.', '["Father, align my desires with Your will","Remove anything that distracts from Your purpose","Keep my focus on eternal things"]'::jsonb, '["I hear God''s voice clearly","I am led by the Holy Spirit","I will not miss my way"]'::jsonb, 'Moses Afolabi'),
