(213, '2026-08-03', 'Heavenly Peace', '{"reference":"Romans 8:28","text":"All things work together for good to those who love God."}'::jsonb, 'The Lord is working behind the scenes on your behalf. What seems like delay is divine preparation. Trust His timing and His methods. He makes all things beautiful in His time.', '["Holy Spirit, lead me in the path of righteousness","Give me wisdom in every decision","Strengthen me for the challenges ahead"]'::jsonb, '["I am more than a conqueror","Nothing shall be impossible for me","I overcome by the blood of the Lamb"]'::jsonb, 'Moses Afolabi'),
