(218, '2026-08-08', 'Perfect Love', '{"reference":"Philippians 4:13","text":"I can do all things through Christ who strengthens me."}'::jsonb, 'Let faith arise in your heart. The same God who parted the Red Sea is able to make a way for you. Nothing is too difficult for Him. Believe and receive His miracle power.', '["Lord, heal every area of brokenness in my life","Restore what the enemy has stolen","Make me whole in Jesus'' name"]'::jsonb, '["Abundance flows to me","My needs are met according to His riches","I am a generous giver"]'::jsonb, 'Moses Afolabi'),
(219, '2026-08-09', 'Abundant Life', '{"reference":"Joshua 1:9","text":"Be strong and courageous. Do not be afraid; do not be discouraged."}'::jsonb, 'Today is a day of divine favor. Doors that were closed are opening. Opportunities are coming your way. Position yourself to receive what God has prepared for you.', '["Father, align my desires with Your will","Remove anything that distracts from Your purpose","Keep my focus on eternal things"]'::jsonb, '["I hear God''s voice clearly","I am led by the Holy Spirit","I will not miss my way"]'::jsonb, 'Moses Afolabi'),
(220, '2026-08-10', 'Faithful Promise', '{"reference":"Psalm 37:4","text":"Delight yourself in the Lord, and he will give you the desires of your heart."}'::jsonb, 'The Holy Spirit is your guide, comforter, and empowerer. Lean into His leading today. He will direct your paths and give you wisdom for every decision.', '["Holy Spirit, fill me afresh today","Use me as a vessel of Your love","Let Your power flow through me"]'::jsonb, '["My family is blessed","Salvation reigns in my household","Generational curses are broken"]'::jsonb, 'Moses Afolabi'),
(221, '2026-08-11', 'Endless Mercy', '{"reference":"Isaiah 40:31","text":"Those who hope in the Lord will renew their strength."}'::jsonb, 'God''s love for you is unconditional and unwavering. You cannot do anything to make Him love you more or less. Rest secure in His perfect love today.', '["Lord, fill me with Your peace that surpasses understanding","Guide my steps according to Your will","Protect me and my loved ones today"]'::jsonb, '["I am blessed and highly favored","God''s grace is upon my life","I walk in divine victory"]'::jsonb, 'Moses Afolabi'),
(222, '2026-08-12', 'Eternal Hope', '{"reference":"John 14:27","text":"Peace I leave with you; my peace I give you."}'::jsonb, 'Prayer changes things. As you bring your concerns to God, trust that He hears and answers. Your prayers are powerful and effective. Keep praying without ceasing.', '["Father, increase my faith to trust You completely","Open doors of opportunity before me","Help me to be a blessing to others"]'::jsonb, '["Today is a day of breakthrough","I receive supernatural favor","My latter is greater than my former"]'::jsonb, 'Moses Afolabi'),
(223, '2026-08-13', 'Righteous Path', '{"reference":"2 Timothy 1:7","text":"God has not given us a spirit of fear, but of power and of love and of a sound mind."}'::jsonb, 'The Word of God is your anchor. Stand firm on His promises, and you will not be shaken. Let Scripture guide your thoughts, words, and actions today.', '["Holy Spirit, lead me in the path of righteousness","Give me wisdom in every decision","Strengthen me for the challenges ahead"]'::jsonb, '["I am more than a conqueror","Nothing shall be impossible for me","I overcome by the blood of the Lamb"]'::jsonb, 'Moses Afolabi'),
(224, '2026-08-14', 'Holy Calling', '{"reference":"Psalm 34:8","text":"Taste and see that the Lord is good; blessed is the one who takes refuge in him."}'::jsonb, 'You are called for such a time as this. God has positioned you strategically for His purposes. Embrace your assignment and fulfill your divine calling.', '["Lord, let Your favor go before me","Remove every obstacle in my path","Crown this day with Your goodness"]'::jsonb, '["The Lord is my shepherd, I lack nothing","Goodness and mercy follow me","I dwell in the house of the Lord"]'::jsonb, 'Moses Afolabi'),
(225, '2026-08-15', 'Sacred Trust', '{"reference":"Romans 12:12","text":"Be joyful in hope, patient in affliction, faithful in prayer."}'::jsonb, 'Mercy triumphs over judgment. Extend grace to others as God has extended grace to you. Forgiveness frees your heart and opens the door to blessing.', '["Father, renew my strength like the eagle","Help me to soar above my circumstances","Fill me with supernatural energy"]'::jsonb, '["I am strong in the Lord","His power works mightily in me","I can do all things through Christ"]'::jsonb, 'Moses Afolabi'),
(226, '2026-08-16', 'Divine Appointment', '{"reference":"Philippians 4:6-7","text":"Do not be anxious about anything, but in every situation, by prayer and petition, with thanksgiving, present your requests to God."}'::jsonb, 'Your latter will be greater than your former. God is doing a new thing in your life. Embrace the changes He is bringing and trust His perfect plan.', '["Lord, give me a grateful heart","Help me to see Your hand in every situation","Let praise continually be on my lips"]'::jsonb, '["My faith pleases God","Mountains move at my command","I speak and things happen"]'::jsonb, 'Moses Afolabi'),
