(228, '2026-08-18', 'Unwavering Faith', '{"reference":"1 John 4:4","text":"Greater is he that is in you than he that is in the world."}'::jsonb, 'The blood of Jesus speaks on your behalf. You are covered, protected, and redeemed. Walk in the confidence of your identity as a child of God.', '["Lord, heal every area of brokenness in my life","Restore what the enemy has stolen","Make me whole in Jesus'' name"]'::jsonb, '["Abundance flows to me","My needs are met according to His riches","I am a generous giver"]'::jsonb, 'Moses Afolabi'),
(229, '2026-08-19', 'Glorious Light', '{"reference":"Psalm 121:1-2","text":"I lift up my eyes to the mountains—where does my help come from? My help comes from the Lord."}'::jsonb, 'Seeds planted in faith will produce a harvest. Be patient and persistent. The fruit of your labor will be manifest in due season. Keep sowing good seeds.', '["Father, align my desires with Your will","Remove anything that distracts from Your purpose","Keep my focus on eternal things"]'::jsonb, '["I hear God''s voice clearly","I am led by the Holy Spirit","I will not miss my way"]'::jsonb, 'Moses Afolabi'),
(230, '2026-08-20', 'Triumphant Spirit', '{"reference":"Colossians 3:15","text":"Let the peace of Christ rule in your hearts."}'::jsonb, 'God''s thoughts toward you are thoughts of peace and not of evil. His plans for you are good. Align your expectations with His promises and watch Him move.', '["Holy Spirit, fill me afresh today","Use me as a vessel of Your love","Let Your power flow through me"]'::jsonb, '["My family is blessed","Salvation reigns in my household","Generational curses are broken"]'::jsonb, 'Moses Afolabi'),
(231, '2026-08-21', 'Healing Power', '{"reference":"James 4:8","text":"Come near to God and he will come near to you."}'::jsonb, 'You are an ambassador of Christ. Everywhere you go, you represent His kingdom. Let your light shine and be a beacon of hope to those around you.', '["Lord, fill me with Your peace that surpasses understanding","Guide my steps according to Your will","Protect me and my loved ones today"]'::jsonb, '["I am blessed and highly favored","God''s grace is upon my life","I walk in divine victory"]'::jsonb, 'Moses Afolabi'),
(232, '2026-08-22', 'Restoration Glory', '{"reference":"Psalm 91:2","text":"I will say of the Lord, ''He is my refuge and my fortress, my God, in whom I trust.''"}'::jsonb, 'Transformation happens from the inside out. Allow the Holy Spirit to renew your mind and transform your heart. Become more like Christ every day.', '["Father, increase my faith to trust You completely","Open doors of opportunity before me","Help me to be a blessing to others"]'::jsonb, '["Today is a day of breakthrough","I receive supernatural favor","My latter is greater than my former"]'::jsonb, 'Moses Afolabi'),
(233, '2026-08-23', 'Covenant Blessing', '{"reference":"Matthew 11:28","text":"Come to me, all you who are weary and burdened, and I will give you rest."}'::jsonb, 'The battle belongs to the Lord. You do not fight alone. Stand firm in faith, and watch God fight on your behalf. Victory is assured.', '["Holy Spirit, lead me in the path of righteousness","Give me wisdom in every decision","Strengthen me for the challenges ahead"]'::jsonb, '["I am more than a conqueror","Nothing shall be impossible for me","I overcome by the blood of the Lamb"]'::jsonb, 'Moses Afolabi'),
(234, '2026-08-24', 'Prophetic Word', '{"reference":"Isaiah 54:17","text":"No weapon formed against you shall prosper."}'::jsonb, 'Every trial is producing perseverance and character in you. Do not despise the process. God is using every circumstance to shape you for greatness.', '["Lord, let Your favor go before me","Remove every obstacle in my path","Crown this day with Your goodness"]'::jsonb, '["The Lord is my shepherd, I lack nothing","Goodness and mercy follow me","I dwell in the house of the Lord"]'::jsonb, 'Moses Afolabi'),
(235, '2026-08-25', 'Anointed Purpose', '{"reference":"Ephesians 3:20","text":"Now to him who is able to do immeasurably more than all we ask or imagine."}'::jsonb, 'Obedience unlocks blessing. When you follow God''s commands, you position yourself in the path of His favor. Choose obedience today.', '["Father, renew my strength like the eagle","Help me to soar above my circumstances","Fill me with supernatural energy"]'::jsonb, '["I am strong in the Lord","His power works mightily in me","I can do all things through Christ"]'::jsonb, 'Moses Afolabi'),
(236, '2026-08-26', 'Overcoming Power', '{"reference":"Psalm 103:1","text":"Bless the Lord, O my soul, and all that is within me, bless his holy name."}'::jsonb, 'The Lord is your healer. Whatever needs restoration in your life—body, soul, or spirit—He is able to make it whole. Receive your healing by faith.', '["Lord, give me a grateful heart","Help me to see Your hand in every situation","Let praise continually be on my lips"]'::jsonb, '["My faith pleases God","Mountains move at my command","I speak and things happen"]'::jsonb, 'Moses Afolabi'),
(237, '2026-08-27', 'Resurrection Life', '{"reference":"Romans 15:13","text":"May the God of hope fill you with all joy and peace as you trust in him."}'::jsonb, 'Unity in the body of Christ brings strength. Stand together with your brothers and sisters in faith. Together, you are stronger and more effective.', '["Father, protect me from the schemes of the enemy","Cover me with Your precious blood","Station Your angels around me"]'::jsonb, '["I am healed by His stripes","Divine health is my portion","Sickness has no place in my body"]'::jsonb, 'Moses Afolabi'),
(238, '2026-08-28', 'Victorious Living', '{"reference":"Psalm 30:5","text":"Weeping may stay for the night, but rejoicing comes in the morning."}'::jsonb, 'God goes before you, making crooked paths straight. He prepares the way for your success. Follow where He leads with confidence and expectation.', '["Lord, heal every area of brokenness in my life","Restore what the enemy has stolen","Make me whole in Jesus'' name"]'::jsonb, '["Abundance flows to me","My needs are met according to His riches","I am a generous giver"]'::jsonb, 'Moses Afolabi'),
(239, '2026-08-29', 'Kingdom Reign', '{"reference":"1 Peter 5:7","text":"Cast all your anxiety on him because he cares for you."}'::jsonb, 'Your testimony is powerful. Share what God has done in your life. Your story has the power to encourage others and bring glory to God.', '["Father, align my desires with Your will","Remove anything that distracts from Your purpose","Keep my focus on eternal things"]'::jsonb, '["I hear God''s voice clearly","I am led by the Holy Spirit","I will not miss my way"]'::jsonb, 'Moses Afolabi'),
(240, '2026-08-30', 'Holy Ground', '{"reference":"Deuteronomy 31:6","text":"Be strong and courageous. The Lord your God goes with you; he will never leave you."}'::jsonb, 'This is a season of breakthrough. Walls are falling, barriers are breaking, and new doors are opening. Step forward boldly into what God has for you.', '["Holy Spirit, fill me afresh today","Use me as a vessel of Your love","Let Your power flow through me"]'::jsonb, '["My family is blessed","Salvation reigns in my household","Generational curses are broken"]'::jsonb, 'Moses Afolabi'),
(241, '2026-08-31', 'Sacred Moment', '{"reference":"Psalm 118:24","text":"This is the day the Lord has made; let us rejoice and be glad in it."}'::jsonb, 'End this month in praise and gratitude. Reflect on God''s faithfulness and look forward with expectation. The best is yet to come.', '["Lord, fill me with Your peace that surpasses understanding","Guide my steps according to Your will","Protect me and my loved ones today"]'::jsonb, '["I am blessed and highly favored","God''s grace is upon my life","I walk in divine victory"]'::jsonb, 'Moses Afolabi'),
(242, '2026-09-01', 'Walking in Victory', '{"reference":"Psalm 23:1","text":"The Lord is my shepherd, I lack nothing."}'::jsonb, 'Today, let the peace of God rule in your heart. Whatever challenges you face, remember that His presence goes with you. He is your shield and your very great reward. Trust in His unfailing love and walk confidently into this day.', '["Lord, fill me with Your peace that surpasses understanding","Guide my steps according to Your will","Protect me and my loved ones today"]'::jsonb, '["I am blessed and highly favored","God''s grace is upon my life","I walk in divine victory"]'::jsonb, 'Moses Afolabi'),
(243, '2026-09-02', 'Divine Favor', '{"reference":"Isaiah 41:10","text":"Fear not, for I am with you; be not dismayed, for I am your God."}'::jsonb, 'God''s promises are yes and amen. Every word He has spoken over your life will come to pass. Hold onto hope, for the One who promised is faithful. Your breakthrough is closer than you think.', '["Father, increase my faith to trust You completely","Open doors of opportunity before me","Help me to be a blessing to others"]'::jsonb, '["Today is a day of breakthrough","I receive supernatural favor","My latter is greater than my former"]'::jsonb, 'Moses Afolabi'),
(244, '2026-09-03', 'Heavenly Peace', '{"reference":"Romans 8:28","text":"All things work together for good to those who love God."}'::jsonb, 'The Lord is working behind the scenes on your behalf. What seems like delay is divine preparation. Trust His timing and His methods. He makes all things beautiful in His time.', '["Holy Spirit, lead me in the path of righteousness","Give me wisdom in every decision","Strengthen me for the challenges ahead"]'::jsonb, '["I am more than a conqueror","Nothing shall be impossible for me","I overcome by the blood of the Lamb"]'::jsonb, 'Moses Afolabi'),
(245, '2026-09-04', 'Abounding Grace', '{"reference":"Jeremiah 33:3","text":"Call to me and I will answer you and tell you great and unsearchable things."}'::jsonb, 'You are more than a conqueror through Christ. Every obstacle is an opportunity for God to show His power. Face today with boldness, knowing that victory is already yours.', '["Lord, let Your favor go before me","Remove every obstacle in my path","Crown this day with Your goodness"]'::jsonb, '["The Lord is my shepherd, I lack nothing","Goodness and mercy follow me","I dwell in the house of the Lord"]'::jsonb, 'Moses Afolabi'),
(246, '2026-09-05', 'Supernatural Joy', '{"reference":"Psalm 46:10","text":"Be still, and know that I am God."}'::jsonb, 'God''s grace is sufficient for every challenge you will encounter today. His strength is made perfect in your weakness. Lean on Him and watch Him carry you through.', '["Father, renew my strength like the eagle","Help me to soar above my circumstances","Fill me with supernatural energy"]'::jsonb, '["I am strong in the Lord","His power works mightily in me","I can do all things through Christ"]'::jsonb, 'Moses Afolabi'),
(247, '2026-09-06', 'Kingdom Authority', '{"reference":"Proverbs 3:5-6","text":"Trust in the Lord with all your heart and lean not on your own understanding."}'::jsonb, 'The joy of the Lord is your strength. Do not let circumstances steal your joy. Choose to rejoice in the Lord always, for He is working all things together for your good.', '["Lord, give me a grateful heart","Help me to see Your hand in every situation","Let praise continually be on my lips"]'::jsonb, '["My faith pleases God","Mountains move at my command","I speak and things happen"]'::jsonb, 'Moses Afolabi'),
(248, '2026-09-07', 'Blessed Assurance', '{"reference":"Matthew 6:33","text":"Seek first his kingdom and his righteousness, and all these things will be given to you."}'::jsonb, 'Heaven is backing you today. Angels are on assignment for your protection and provision. Walk in confidence, knowing that the Creator of the universe is fighting for you.', '["Father, protect me from the schemes of the enemy","Cover me with Your precious blood","Station Your angels around me"]'::jsonb, '["I am healed by His stripes","Divine health is my portion","Sickness has no place in my body"]'::jsonb, 'Moses Afolabi'),
(249, '2026-09-08', 'Perfect Love', '{"reference":"Philippians 4:13","text":"I can do all things through Christ who strengthens me."}'::jsonb, 'Let faith arise in your heart. The same God who parted the Red Sea is able to make a way for you. Nothing is too difficult for Him. Believe and receive His miracle power.', '["Lord, heal every area of brokenness in my life","Restore what the enemy has stolen","Make me whole in Jesus'' name"]'::jsonb, '["Abundance flows to me","My needs are met according to His riches","I am a generous giver"]'::jsonb, 'Moses Afolabi'),
(250, '2026-09-09', 'Abundant Life', '{"reference":"Joshua 1:9","text":"Be strong and courageous. Do not be afraid; do not be discouraged."}'::jsonb, 'Today is a day of divine favor. Doors that were closed are opening. Opportunities are coming your way. Position yourself to receive what God has prepared for you.', '["Father, align my desires with Your will","Remove anything that distracts from Your purpose","Keep my focus on eternal things"]'::jsonb, '["I hear God''s voice clearly","I am led by the Holy Spirit","I will not miss my way"]'::jsonb, 'Moses Afolabi'),
(251, '2026-09-10', 'Faithful Promise', '{"reference":"Psalm 37:4","text":"Delight yourself in the Lord, and he will give you the desires of your heart."}'::jsonb, 'The Holy Spirit is your guide, comforter, and empowerer. Lean into His leading today. He will direct your paths and give you wisdom for every decision.', '["Holy Spirit, fill me afresh today","Use me as a vessel of Your love","Let Your power flow through me"]'::jsonb, '["My family is blessed","Salvation reigns in my household","Generational curses are broken"]'::jsonb, 'Moses Afolabi'),
(252, '2026-09-11', 'Endless Mercy', '{"reference":"Isaiah 40:31","text":"Those who hope in the Lord will renew their strength."}'::jsonb, 'God''s love for you is unconditional and unwavering. You cannot do anything to make Him love you more or less. Rest secure in His perfect love today.', '["Lord, fill me with Your peace that surpasses understanding","Guide my steps according to Your will","Protect me and my loved ones today"]'::jsonb, '["I am blessed and highly favored","God''s grace is upon my life","I walk in divine victory"]'::jsonb, 'Moses Afolabi'),
(253, '2026-09-12', 'Eternal Hope', '{"reference":"John 14:27","text":"Peace I leave with you; my peace I give you."}'::jsonb, 'Prayer changes things. As you bring your concerns to God, trust that He hears and answers. Your prayers are powerful and effective. Keep praying without ceasing.', '["Father, increase my faith to trust You completely","Open doors of opportunity before me","Help me to be a blessing to others"]'::jsonb, '["Today is a day of breakthrough","I receive supernatural favor","My latter is greater than my former"]'::jsonb, 'Moses Afolabi'),
(254, '2026-09-13', 'Righteous Path', '{"reference":"2 Timothy 1:7","text":"God has not given us a spirit of fear, but of power and of love and of a sound mind."}'::jsonb, 'The Word of God is your anchor. Stand firm on His promises, and you will not be shaken. Let Scripture guide your thoughts, words, and actions today.', '["Holy Spirit, lead me in the path of righteousness","Give me wisdom in every decision","Strengthen me for the challenges ahead"]'::jsonb, '["I am more than a conqueror","Nothing shall be impossible for me","I overcome by the blood of the Lamb"]'::jsonb, 'Moses Afolabi'),
(255, '2026-09-14', 'Holy Calling', '{"reference":"Psalm 34:8","text":"Taste and see that the Lord is good; blessed is the one who takes refuge in him."}'::jsonb, 'You are called for such a time as this. God has positioned you strategically for His purposes. Embrace your assignment and fulfill your divine calling.', '["Lord, let Your favor go before me","Remove every obstacle in my path","Crown this day with Your goodness"]'::jsonb, '["The Lord is my shepherd, I lack nothing","Goodness and mercy follow me","I dwell in the house of the Lord"]'::jsonb, 'Moses Afolabi'),
(256, '2026-09-15', 'Sacred Trust', '{"reference":"Romans 12:12","text":"Be joyful in hope, patient in affliction, faithful in prayer."}'::jsonb, 'Mercy triumphs over judgment. Extend grace to others as God has extended grace to you. Forgiveness frees your heart and opens the door to blessing.', '["Father, renew my strength like the eagle","Help me to soar above my circumstances","Fill me with supernatural energy"]'::jsonb, '["I am strong in the Lord","His power works mightily in me","I can do all things through Christ"]'::jsonb, 'Moses Afolabi'),
(257, '2026-09-16', 'Divine Appointment', '{"reference":"Philippians 4:6-7","text":"Do not be anxious about anything, but in every situation, by prayer and petition, with thanksgiving, present your requests to God."}'::jsonb, 'Your latter will be greater than your former. God is doing a new thing in your life. Embrace the changes He is bringing and trust His perfect plan.', '["Lord, give me a grateful heart","Help me to see Your hand in every situation","Let praise continually be on my lips"]'::jsonb, '["My faith pleases God","Mountains move at my command","I speak and things happen"]'::jsonb, 'Moses Afolabi'),
(258, '2026-09-17', 'Spiritual Strength', '{"reference":"Hebrews 11:6","text":"Without faith it is impossible to please God."}'::jsonb, 'Worship unlocks heaven''s resources. As you praise God in every situation, you create an atmosphere for miracles. Let praise be your first response today.', '["Father, protect me from the schemes of the enemy","Cover me with Your precious blood","Station Your angels around me"]'::jsonb, '["I am healed by His stripes","Divine health is my portion","Sickness has no place in my body"]'::jsonb, 'Moses Afolabi'),
(259, '2026-09-18', 'Unwavering Faith', '{"reference":"1 John 4:4","text":"Greater is he that is in you than he that is in the world."}'::jsonb, 'The blood of Jesus speaks on your behalf. You are covered, protected, and redeemed. Walk in the confidence of your identity as a child of God.', '["Lord, heal every area of brokenness in my life","Restore what the enemy has stolen","Make me whole in Jesus'' name"]'::jsonb, '["Abundance flows to me","My needs are met according to His riches","I am a generous giver"]'::jsonb, 'Moses Afolabi'),
(260, '2026-09-19', 'Glorious Light', '{"reference":"Psalm 121:1-2","text":"I lift up my eyes to the mountains—where does my help come from? My help comes from the Lord."}'::jsonb, 'Seeds planted in faith will produce a harvest. Be patient and persistent. The fruit of your labor will be manifest in due season. Keep sowing good seeds.', '["Father, align my desires with Your will","Remove anything that distracts from Your purpose","Keep my focus on eternal things"]'::jsonb, '["I hear God''s voice clearly","I am led by the Holy Spirit","I will not miss my way"]'::jsonb, 'Moses Afolabi'),
(261, '2026-09-20', 'Triumphant Spirit', '{"reference":"Colossians 3:15","text":"Let the peace of Christ rule in your hearts."}'::jsonb, 'God''s thoughts toward you are thoughts of peace and not of evil. His plans for you are good. Align your expectations with His promises and watch Him move.', '["Holy Spirit, fill me afresh today","Use me as a vessel of Your love","Let Your power flow through me"]'::jsonb, '["My family is blessed","Salvation reigns in my household","Generational curses are broken"]'::jsonb, 'Moses Afolabi'),
(262, '2026-09-21', 'Healing Power', '{"reference":"James 4:8","text":"Come near to God and he will come near to you."}'::jsonb, 'You are an ambassador of Christ. Everywhere you go, you represent His kingdom. Let your light shine and be a beacon of hope to those around you.', '["Lord, fill me with Your peace that surpasses understanding","Guide my steps according to Your will","Protect me and my loved ones today"]'::jsonb, '["I am blessed and highly favored","God''s grace is upon my life","I walk in divine victory"]'::jsonb, 'Moses Afolabi'),
(263, '2026-09-22', 'Restoration Glory', '{"reference":"Psalm 91:2","text":"I will say of the Lord, ''He is my refuge and my fortress, my God, in whom I trust.''"}'::jsonb, 'Transformation happens from the inside out. Allow the Holy Spirit to renew your mind and transform your heart. Become more like Christ every day.', '["Father, increase my faith to trust You completely","Open doors of opportunity before me","Help me to be a blessing to others"]'::jsonb, '["Today is a day of breakthrough","I receive supernatural favor","My latter is greater than my former"]'::jsonb, 'Moses Afolabi'),
