(285, '2026-10-14', 'Holy Calling', '{"reference":"Psalm 34:8","text":"Taste and see that the Lord is good; blessed is the one who takes refuge in him."}'::jsonb, 'You are called for such a time as this. God has positioned you strategically for His purposes. Embrace your assignment and fulfill your divine calling.', '["Lord, let Your favor go before me","Remove every obstacle in my path","Crown this day with Your goodness"]'::jsonb, '["The Lord is my shepherd, I lack nothing","Goodness and mercy follow me","I dwell in the house of the Lord"]'::jsonb, 'Moses Afolabi'),
