(290, '2026-10-19', 'Glorious Light', '{"reference":"Psalm 121:1-2","text":"I lift up my eyes to the mountains—where does my help come from? My help comes from the Lord."}'::jsonb, 'Seeds planted in faith will produce a harvest. Be patient and persistent. The fruit of your labor will be manifest in due season. Keep sowing good seeds.', '["Father, align my desires with Your will","Remove anything that distracts from Your purpose","Keep my focus on eternal things"]'::jsonb, '["I hear God''s voice clearly","I am led by the Holy Spirit","I will not miss my way"]'::jsonb, 'Moses Afolabi'),
(291, '2026-10-20', 'Triumphant Spirit', '{"reference":"Colossians 3:15","text":"Let the peace of Christ rule in your hearts."}'::jsonb, 'God''s thoughts toward you are thoughts of peace and not of evil. His plans for you are good. Align your expectations with His promises and watch Him move.', '["Holy Spirit, fill me afresh today","Use me as a vessel of Your love","Let Your power flow through me"]'::jsonb, '["My family is blessed","Salvation reigns in my household","Generational curses are broken"]'::jsonb, 'Moses Afolabi'),
(292, '2026-10-21', 'Healing Power', '{"reference":"James 4:8","text":"Come near to God and he will come near to you."}'::jsonb, 'You are an ambassador of Christ. Everywhere you go, you represent His kingdom. Let your light shine and be a beacon of hope to those around you.', '["Lord, fill me with Your peace that surpasses understanding","Guide my steps according to Your will","Protect me and my loved ones today"]'::jsonb, '["I am blessed and highly favored","God''s grace is upon my life","I walk in divine victory"]'::jsonb, 'Moses Afolabi'),
(293, '2026-10-22', 'Restoration Glory', '{"reference":"Psalm 91:2","text":"I will say of the Lord, ''He is my refuge and my fortress, my God, in whom I trust.''"}'::jsonb, 'Transformation happens from the inside out. Allow the Holy Spirit to renew your mind and transform your heart. Become more like Christ every day.', '["Father, increase my faith to trust You completely","Open doors of opportunity before me","Help me to be a blessing to others"]'::jsonb, '["Today is a day of breakthrough","I receive supernatural favor","My latter is greater than my former"]'::jsonb, 'Moses Afolabi'),
(294, '2026-10-23', 'Covenant Blessing', '{"reference":"Matthew 11:28","text":"Come to me, all you who are weary and burdened, and I will give you rest."}'::jsonb, 'The battle belongs to the Lord. You do not fight alone. Stand firm in faith, and watch God fight on your behalf. Victory is assured.', '["Holy Spirit, lead me in the path of righteousness","Give me wisdom in every decision","Strengthen me for the challenges ahead"]'::jsonb, '["I am more than a conqueror","Nothing shall be impossible for me","I overcome by the blood of the Lamb"]'::jsonb, 'Moses Afolabi'),
(295, '2026-10-24', 'Prophetic Word', '{"reference":"Isaiah 54:17","text":"No weapon formed against you shall prosper."}'::jsonb, 'Every trial is producing perseverance and character in you. Do not despise the process. God is using every circumstance to shape you for greatness.', '["Lord, let Your favor go before me","Remove every obstacle in my path","Crown this day with Your goodness"]'::jsonb, '["The Lord is my shepherd, I lack nothing","Goodness and mercy follow me","I dwell in the house of the Lord"]'::jsonb, 'Moses Afolabi'),
(296, '2026-10-25', 'Anointed Purpose', '{"reference":"Ephesians 3:20","text":"Now to him who is able to do immeasurably more than all we ask or imagine."}'::jsonb, 'Obedience unlocks blessing. When you follow God''s commands, you position yourself in the path of His favor. Choose obedience today.', '["Father, renew my strength like the eagle","Help me to soar above my circumstances","Fill me with supernatural energy"]'::jsonb, '["I am strong in the Lord","His power works mightily in me","I can do all things through Christ"]'::jsonb, 'Moses Afolabi'),
(297, '2026-10-26', 'Overcoming Power', '{"reference":"Psalm 103:1","text":"Bless the Lord, O my soul, and all that is within me, bless his holy name."}'::jsonb, 'The Lord is your healer. Whatever needs restoration in your life—body, soul, or spirit—He is able to make it whole. Receive your healing by faith.', '["Lord, give me a grateful heart","Help me to see Your hand in every situation","Let praise continually be on my lips"]'::jsonb, '["My faith pleases God","Mountains move at my command","I speak and things happen"]'::jsonb, 'Moses Afolabi'),
(298, '2026-10-27', 'Resurrection Life', '{"reference":"Romans 15:13","text":"May the God of hope fill you with all joy and peace as you trust in him."}'::jsonb, 'Unity in the body of Christ brings strength. Stand together with your brothers and sisters in faith. Together, you are stronger and more effective.', '["Father, protect me from the schemes of the enemy","Cover me with Your precious blood","Station Your angels around me"]'::jsonb, '["I am healed by His stripes","Divine health is my portion","Sickness has no place in my body"]'::jsonb, 'Moses Afolabi'),
(299, '2026-10-28', 'Victorious Living', '{"reference":"Psalm 30:5","text":"Weeping may stay for the night, but rejoicing comes in the morning."}'::jsonb, 'God goes before you, making crooked paths straight. He prepares the way for your success. Follow where He leads with confidence and expectation.', '["Lord, heal every area of brokenness in my life","Restore what the enemy has stolen","Make me whole in Jesus'' name"]'::jsonb, '["Abundance flows to me","My needs are met according to His riches","I am a generous giver"]'::jsonb, 'Moses Afolabi'),
(300, '2026-10-29', 'Kingdom Reign', '{"reference":"1 Peter 5:7","text":"Cast all your anxiety on him because he cares for you."}'::jsonb, 'Your testimony is powerful. Share what God has done in your life. Your story has the power to encourage others and bring glory to God.', '["Father, align my desires with Your will","Remove anything that distracts from Your purpose","Keep my focus on eternal things"]'::jsonb, '["I hear God''s voice clearly","I am led by the Holy Spirit","I will not miss my way"]'::jsonb, 'Moses Afolabi'),
(301, '2026-10-30', 'Holy Ground', '{"reference":"Deuteronomy 31:6","text":"Be strong and courageous. The Lord your God goes with you; he will never leave you."}'::jsonb, 'This is a season of breakthrough. Walls are falling, barriers are breaking, and new doors are opening. Step forward boldly into what God has for you.', '["Holy Spirit, fill me afresh today","Use me as a vessel of Your love","Let Your power flow through me"]'::jsonb, '["My family is blessed","Salvation reigns in my household","Generational curses are broken"]'::jsonb, 'Moses Afolabi'),
