(303, '2026-11-01', 'Walking in Victory', '{"reference":"Psalm 23:1","text":"The Lord is my shepherd, I lack nothing."}'::jsonb, 'Today, let the peace of God rule in your heart. Whatever challenges you face, remember that His presence goes with you. He is your shield and your very great reward. Trust in His unfailing love and walk confidently into this day.', '["Lord, fill me with Your peace that surpasses understanding","Guide my steps according to Your will","Protect me and my loved ones today"]'::jsonb, '["I am blessed and highly favored","God''s grace is upon my life","I walk in divine victory"]'::jsonb, 'Moses Afolabi'),
(304, '2026-11-02', 'Divine Favor', '{"reference":"Isaiah 41:10","text":"Fear not, for I am with you; be not dismayed, for I am your God."}'::jsonb, 'God''s promises are yes and amen. Every word He has spoken over your life will come to pass. Hold onto hope, for the One who promised is faithful. Your breakthrough is closer than you think.', '["Father, increase my faith to trust You completely","Open doors of opportunity before me","Help me to be a blessing to others"]'::jsonb, '["Today is a day of breakthrough","I receive supernatural favor","My latter is greater than my former"]'::jsonb, 'Moses Afolabi'),
(305, '2026-11-03', 'Heavenly Peace', '{"reference":"Romans 8:28","text":"All things work together for good to those who love God."}'::jsonb, 'The Lord is working behind the scenes on your behalf. What seems like delay is divine preparation. Trust His timing and His methods. He makes all things beautiful in His time.', '["Holy Spirit, lead me in the path of righteousness","Give me wisdom in every decision","Strengthen me for the challenges ahead"]'::jsonb, '["I am more than a conqueror","Nothing shall be impossible for me","I overcome by the blood of the Lamb"]'::jsonb, 'Moses Afolabi'),
