(367, '2027-01-04', 'Friend of God', '{"reference":"James 2:23","text":"And the scripture was fulfilled which saith, Abraham believed God, and it was imputed unto him for righteousness: and he was called the Friend of God."}'::jsonb, 'The words of James 2:23 carry a powerful message for believers today. And the scripture was fulfilled which saith, Abraham believed God, and it was imputed unto him for righteousness: and he was called the Friend of God. This truth is not merely historical; it is a living reality that shapes our daily walk with God.

