God''s faithfulness is demonstrated throughout the ages. From generation to generation, He has proven Himself true to His Word. What He promised, He fulfills. What He declared, He brings to pass.', '["Father, help me to truly understand and live out the truth of James 3:5-6","Lord, let the reality of controlling speech transform my daily walk with You","Holy Spirit, open my eyes to see the depth of wisdom in this passage from James","God, remove every hindrance that prevents me from fully embracing this truth","Lord, let Your Word concerning controlling speech produce lasting fruit in my life","Father, strengthen my faith as I meditate on Your promises in James","Lord Jesus, help me to be a living example of controlling speech to those around me"]'::jsonb, '["I declare that controlling speech is my reality in Christ Jesus","I walk in the truth of James 3:5-6 every day of my life","By faith, I receive every blessing that God has prepared for me","I am established in the Word of God and nothing shall move me","The power of God works mightily in me and through me","\"Let God''s promises shine on your problems.\" — Corrie ten Boom","\"Worry does not empty tomorrow of its sorrow, it empties today of its strength.\" — Corrie ten Boom","\"There is not one blade of grass, there is no color in this world that is not intended to make us rejoice.\" — John Calvin","I prophesy over my life: the word of God concerning controlling speech is established and cannot be reversed","I decree and declare that every plan of the enemy against my destiny is destroyed by the power of God''s Word"]'::jsonb, 'Moses Afolabi'),
(369, '2027-01-06', 'Blessing Not Cursing', '{"reference":"James 3:10","text":"Out of the same mouth proceedeth blessing and cursing. My brethren, these things ought not so to be."}'::jsonb, 'The words of James 3:10 carry a powerful message for believers today. Out of the same mouth proceedeth blessing and cursing. My brethren, these things ought not so to be. This truth is not merely historical; it is a living reality that shapes our daily walk with God.

